metadata.name: LIT: Rekindled
metadata.description:
We present ‘LIT: Rekindled’ by rata_yonqui with gratitude and appreciation to our LITIZENS who have stood by us through thick and thin. It is a testament to the steadfast commitment of our LITIZENS, a statement of the shared vision that has brought us together, and a manifestation of our ongoing commitment to nurturing the flame of LIT.  
LIT: Rekindled will stand as a beacon that marks the beginning of a new era in which LIT evolves and flourishes with a stronger community voice. Let it stand as a symbol of our collective strength, and as a reminder of the incredible things that we can accomplish when we work together with purpose and determination.
